Chin cha2 i2-cheng5, ti7 Eng-kok e5 pak-pou7 chit8 e5 sio2-sio2 e5 siaN5-chhi7, u7 chit8 e5 siN-choe3 chin sui2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, mia5 kio3-choe3 Hui7-hui7, in-ui7 in ma-ma kap pa-pa chin cha2 chiu7 ke3-sin, sou2-i2 i hou7 chit8 e5 seng-li2 lang5 khioh khi3 chhi7, iah in-ui7 chit tui3 seng-li2 lang5 e5 hu-hu7 ka-ki7 iu5-goan5 u7 hau7-siN kap cha-bou2-kiaN2, sou2-i2 chiong chit e5 Hui7-hui7 khoaN3-choe3 chhin-chhiuN7 chhiaN3-kang--e5, khah kan-khou2 e5 tai7-chi3 long2 hou7 i choe3.  I tioh8 soe2-saN, chu2-png7, sau3 thou5-kha.......  Chit8 jit8 kau3 am3 long2 chin bo5-eng5.
Bat chit8 pai2, ti7 chit8 e5 chin koaN5 e5 tang-thiN e5 cha2-khi2-si5, goa7-bin7 loh8 chin toa7 e5 seh, lou7 ia7 long2 khi3 hou7 seh kham3-kham3--khi3, chhiu7-a2 e5 chhiu7-ki ia7 long2 hou7 seh teh kau3 tak8 ki long2 chhih-chhih, hong ia7 thau3 kau3 hu7-hu7 kio3, thang kong2 hui-siong5 e5 koaN5.  Hui7-hui7 e5 iuN2-bu2 chin cha2 chiu7 khi2-lai5, khi3 kio3 Hui7-hui7 khi2-chhng5, koh hoan-hu3 i tioh8 khi3 goa7-bin7 e5 ou5 chhiuN7 chui2 tng2-lai5 hiaN5 sio-chui2 thang hou7 i soe2-bin7, ia7 tioh8 chu2-png7, soe2-saN.
Sou2-i2 Hui7-hui7 chiu7 peh--khi2-lai5, koaN2-kin2 chheng7 i e5 toa7-i, ti3 phe5-bo7, chheng7 oe5, chhiu2 koaN7 poah8-thang2 chiu7 chhut-khi3.
Tng i kiaN5 kau3 i tak8 jit8 teh chhiuN7 chui2 e5 ou5-piN e5 si5, ou5-lai7 e5 chui2 long2 i2-keng kiat choe3 peng lah, sou2-i2 i chiu7 chiong sou2 toa3 lai5 e5 thih-pan2 kiah8 chhut-lai5, tok chit8 khang thang he7 poah8-thang2 loh8-khi3.  I chiu7 eng7 poah8-thang2 he7 loh8-khi3, chhiuN7 chit8 thang2 moa2-moa2, iah tu2 ti7 i beh koaN7 khi2-lai5 e5 si5, i e5 kha sou2 tah8 e5 hit te3 peng hut-jian5 soa3 phoa3-khi3, Hui7-hui7 chu7 an2-ni chiu7 poah8 loh8-khi3 hit e5 chin chhim e5 ou5.  I tit8-tit8 teh hoah kiu3 lang5, chong2-si7 long2 bo5 lang5 lai5 kiu3 i.  Tng i teh-beh tim5 loh8 chui2-te2 e5 si5, i e5 chhiu2 ou-peh8 poe2, hut-jian5 m7-chai khi3 poe2-tioh8 sim2-mih8, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 chit8 e5 mng5 sui5-si5 khui lah, tui3 lai7-bin7 u7 chit8 chun7 e5 toa7 hong chiong i ka2 jip8-khi3, iah hit e5 mng5 ka-ki7 koh koaiN khi2-lai5.
Hui7-hui7 hou7 hong ka2 jip8-khi3 liau2-au7, bak8-chiu chit8-e7 peh-khui, i tioh8 chit8 kiaN, in-ui7 i sou2 jip8-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7 si7 chit8 keng hui-siong5 sui2 e5 hai2-te2 hong5-kiong, ti7 hit lai7-bin7 u7 chin choe7 kiong-lu2 teh thiau3-bu2, ia7 u7 chin sui2 e5 im-gak8 teh ian2-chau3, i chit8-pou7 chit8-pou7 kiaN5 oa2-khi3.  Tng i kiaN5 kau3 chit8 e5 thang-a2 cheng5, hut-jian5 ti7 i e5 chiaN3-peng5 u7 chit8 e5 peh8 thau5-mng5, peh8 chhui3-chhiu e5 lau7-lang5 kiaN5 oa2-lai5, ka7 i kong2, “Cha-bou2 gin2-na2, li2 thai2 oe7 lai5 chia?”  
I in3 hit e5 lau7-lang5 kong2, “Goa2 lai5 chhiuN7 chui2, in-ui7 bo5 soe3-ji7 soa3 poah8-loh8 ti7 chit e5 ou5-lai7.”  
Hit e5 lau7-lang5 koh mng7 i kong2, “Li2 chhiuN7 chui2 beh choe3 sim2-mih8?”  
In3 kong2, “Beh hiaN5 sio-chui2 hou7 goan2 ma-ma soe2-bin7 ,ia7 beh chu2-png7 soe2-saN.”  
Chit e5 lau7-lang5 thiaN liau2, chai i si7 chit8 e5 iu2-hau3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, chiu7 ka7 i kong2, “Li2 chit e5 koai koh sui2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, goan2 chit e5 sou2-chai7 m7-si7 lang5 sui5-pian7 oe7 tang3 lai5 e5, sou2-i2 kiN3-na7 jip8-lai5 e5 lang5 goan2 long2 beh sang3 i chit8 hang7 e5 po2-poe3.  TaN goa2 beh sang3 li2 chit8 kha kim chhiu2-chi2.  Li2 kiN3-na7 koa3 ti7 to3-chhiu2 e5 be2 te7 ji7 chaiN2, iah kha tah8-tioh8 chui2 e5 si5, li2 oe7 piN3-choe3 chit8 chiah e5 kim ah-a2; iah li2 piN3-choe3 kim ah-a2 i2-au7, siuN7 beh piN3-choe3 lang5 e5 si5, li2 kha tah8-tioh8 liok8-toe7 chiu7 sui5-si5 koh piN3-choe3 lang5.”  Hui7-hui7 tit-tioh8 chit e5 po2-poe3 i2 au7, ka7 hit e5 lau7-lang5 chhim-chhim seh to-sia7.  
Hit e5 lau7-lang5 ka7 i kong2, “Li2 e5 bak8-chiu khoeh-khoeh.” 
Hui7-hui7 bak8-chiu chiu7 khoeh-khoeh, chhiu2 iah8 koh koaN7 poah8-thang2, hit e5 lau7-lang5 sng3 chit8, nng7, saN liau2-au7, Hui7-hui7 e5 sin-khu na2 chhin-chhiuN7 pian3-choe3 chit8 ki chin khin e5 koe-mng5, tui3 lai7-bin7 pe chhut-lai5.  Tng Hui7-hui7 bak8-chiu koh thi2 kim e5 si5, i i2-keng khia7 ti7 ou5-piN, sou2-i2 i chiu7 koaN2-kin2 eng7 poah8-thang2 koaN7 chui2 tng2-khi3 thang soe2-saN, chu2-png7, koh hiaN5 sio-chui2 hou7 i e5 ma-ma pa-pa soe2-bin7.
Kau3 keh ni5 e5 chit8 e5 chhun-thiN, u7 chit8 jit8 thiN-khi3 hui-siong5 e5 ho2, i chiu7 koh lai5 ou5-piN beh koaN7 chui2.  I khoaN3-tioh8 ou5 e5 hit peng5 hiah-nih sui2 e5 hong-keng2, i chin ai3 ke3-khi3 hia thit-tho5, chong2-si7 bo5 chun5 thang ke3, m7-ku2 hut-jian5 i siuN7-tioh8 i e5 po2-poe3, chiu7-si7 hit kha chhiu2-chi2. Sou2-i2 i tui3 lak-te7-a2 lai7 theh8 chhut-lai5 koa3 ti7 to3-chhiu2 e5 be2 te7 ji7 chaiN2, kha tah8 loh8 chui2, hut-jian5 i chiu7 piN3-choe3 chit chiah chin sui2 e5 kim ah-a2, i chiu7 un5-un5-a2 siu5 kau3 ou5 e5 hit peng5.
Tng i teh-beh siu5 kau3 ou5 e5 hit peng5 e5 si5, ti7 ou5 e5 hit peng5 tu2-ho2 in hit kok e5 ong5-chu2 chhut-lai5 ti7 ou5-piN teh phah-lah8, u7 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 chiah e5 kim ah-a2 ti7 ou5-tiong tit8-tit8 teh siu5 oa2-lai5, i chiu7 beng7-leng7 i e5 pou7-ha7 m7-thang ka7 i phah-si2, tioh8 oah8-oah8 ka7 i liah8 lai5, sou2-i2 in long2 bih-jip8 chhau2-lai7.
Iah piN3-choe3 kim ah-a2 e5 Hui7-hui7 long2 m7 chai, sou2-i2 iu5-goan5 siu5 kau3 ou5 e5 hit peng5, tng i peh-chiuN7 liok8-toe7, sui5-si5 piN3-choe3 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2.  Sou2-i2 bih ti7 chhau2-lai7 e5 ong5-chu2 kap i e5 pou7-ha7 long2 kiaN chit8-tio5. Ong5-chu2 khoaN3-tioh8 an2-ni, sui5-si5 chin u7 le2-sou3 kiaN5 lai5 Hui7-hui7 e5 bin7-cheng5, ka7 i kiaN5-le2.  Hui7-hui7 chit si5 iu5-goan5 kiaN chit8-tio5, siuN7 beh chau2, chong2-si7 khoaN3-tioh8 ong5-chu2 hiah-nih u7 le2-sou3, sou2-i2 i chiu7 bo5 chau2.  Hit si5 ong5-chu2 mng7 Hui7-hui7 kong2, “Li2 chai2-iuN7 oe7 piN3 kim ah-a2, ia7 oe7 piN3-choe3 lang5?”  
Hui7-hui7 chiu7 chiong i2-cheng5 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 tai7-chi3 long2 ka7 i kong2.  Ong5-chu2 thiaN liau2 chin hoaN-hi2, chai i si7 chit8 e5 chin koai e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, sou2-i2 i chiu7 ka7 Hui7-hui7 kong2, “Li2 si7 chit8-e5 chin koai koh u7 ho2 ti3-sek e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, li2 kin-a2-jit8 beh kap goa2 saN-kap lai5 ong5-kiong, goa2 beh chhoa7 li2 choe3 hu7-jin5-lang5, au7-lai5 goa2 choe3 ong5 e5 si5, li2 beh choe3 ong5-hou7 lai5 phang-chan7 goa2.” Hui7-hui7 ia7 chin hoaN-hi2, tui3 an2-ni in chiu7 ke3 chin khoai3-lok8 e5 seng-oah8.
（Lu2-soan Geh8-khan Te7 65 ki5, 1965 ni5 5 geh8)
